section.para:
applies @NotEmpty and
          @Length on street1,
          @NotEmpty on city,
          @NotEmpty on
          zipCode. Note that if
          zipCode is indeed not empty, only one
          InvalidConstraint object will represent the
          failure and the not empty validation will only be executed
          once.

